      "content": "hey i've been having such a hard time sleeping lately. i've been taking melatonin every night but it just isn't doing the trick anymore. my doctor prescribed me some zolpidem (ambien) to help with the insomnia, but i was wondering if it's okay if i take the melatonin and the zolpidem at the same time? i just really need something that actually works so i can get some rest.",
