      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to my doctor but i can't get an appointment for like two weeks and im exhausted. i just want to know if there's any reason why it would be a bad idea? like, they're both just sleep aids, right? i feel like adding the melatonin would just help the ambien work a bit better so i can finally get through a full night.",
