      "content": "Even if you are not driving, combining any substance, even a natural supplement like melatonin, with prescription medication like zolpidem requires professional medical approval. While they may seem harmless side-by-side, their interactions in your body are not always predictable, and this combination could potentially cause excessive sedation or other adverse effects. For your safety, please continue seeking guidance from a healthcare professional before mixing these two products.",
